\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dd z_{i}=\dfrac{\dd\ell_{i}}{\ell_{i}}\left(z_{b}-z_{a}\right)
\]

\end_inset

(notemos que este incremento es 
\emph on
negativo
\emph default
, pues 
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

